About us
The Big 10 Tavern, your go-to spot for a week full of entertainment and delicious bites!
Join us every Tuesday for an exciting game of Bingo starting at 6 PM. On Wednesdays, it's your time to shine with Karaoke from 7 to 9 PM. Challenge your knowledge on Thursdays with Trivia at 6 PM.
Our lively atmosphere is complemented by daily food specials, ensuring there's something to tantalize your taste buds every day. Don't miss our Happy Hour deals and the warmth of our friendly staff. Come experience the fun and flavors at Big 10 Tavern!
